61.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095818\/bedroom-storage-units-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Smart bedrooms make for a clean space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Multi-Functional Tv Storage Unit With Hidden Storage Space<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Installing a multi-functional <strong>TV storage unit<\/strong> into your living space is like introducing a magician&#8217;s hat, where you can hide away all the clutter associated with home entertainment. They often serve multiple purposes, equipped with cabinets or shelves for storing media equipment, such as DVD players, gaming consoles, and sound systems, keeping these essential components organised and out of sight when not in use. Some units even offer space for books or additional storage, making them versatile additions to your living space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095808\/tv-storage-units.jpg\" alt=\"TV storage unit with hidden space which is multi-functional\" class=\"wp-image-52154\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095808\/tv-storage-units.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095808\/tv-storage-units-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095808\/tv-storage-units-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095808\/tv-storage-units-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Amp up space with a TV storage unit <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Sleek Cabinet Storage Unit to Create an Illusion of Space\u00a0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Floating cabinets or wall-mounted units create the illusion of a more spacious room. Install a cabinet storage unit in the living room, kitchen, or bathroom to store items and keep the floor area free from bulky furniture. The decision to have a <strong>cabinet storage unit<\/strong> or wall storage unit in your living space is akin to a design-savvy sleight of hand, where your room seemingly expands before your eyes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095759\/cabinet-storage-units.jpg\" alt=\"Cabinet storage unit for a sleek look to elevate the aesthetics\" class=\"wp-image-52153\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095759\/cabinet-storage-units.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095759\/cabinet-storage-units-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095759\/cabinet-storage-units-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095759\/cabinet-storage-units-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Elevate the aesthetics of your small space with clever designs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Corner Storage Unit for Forgotten Nooks\u00a0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Transform overlooked corners into organised, efficient and aesthetically pleasing storage solutions. A <strong>corner storage unit<\/strong> comes in various styles and materials, allowing you to choose designs that harmonise with your home&#8217;s overall look and feel. These can be helpful <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/bathroom-storage-ideas\/\"><strong>bathroom storage units<\/strong><\/a> or add efficiency to small kitchen spaces. Whether you prefer a rustic wooden shelf or a modern metal unit, these pieces can complement your existing decor or create a stylish contrast, adding depth and character to your space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095751\/corner-storage-units.jpg\" alt=\"Corner storage unit which is efficient and aesthetically pleasing\" class=\"wp-image-52152\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095751\/corner-storage-units.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095751\/corner-storage-units-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095751\/corner-storage-units-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095751\/corner-storage-units-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Never waste space!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Smart Space-Saving Crockery Storage Unit for Delicate Pieces<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Due to its delicate beauty and sentimental worth, crockery pieces demand a storage solution that not only protects them but also maximises space in your home. A clever space-saving crockery storage unit is a game-changer in the field of tableware organisation that combines practicality and sophistication.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095742\/crockery-storage-units.jpg\" alt=\"Crockery storage unit for delicate pieces which is smart and space-saving\" class=\"wp-image-52151\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095742\/crockery-storage-units.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/04095742\/crockery-storage-units-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/1